<div class="imageWithCaptionLeft" id="asset-47096">
<figure>
<img alt="individual standing next to a pile of electronic waste, illustration" src="/system/assets/0004/7096/021624_CACMpg14_Mitigate-EWaste.large.jpg?1708108310&amp;1708108310" title="individual standing next to a pile of electronic waste, illustration" />
